in":20082,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Silence: Allah is silent on matters for your benefit","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 19, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhat Allah has made lawful in his book is lawful, and what he has made unlawful is unlawful. Whatever he has remained silent upon, it is for your benefit, so accept benefit from Allah. Verily, Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33929,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/15\/shafii-on-criticism\/","url_meta":{"origin":20082,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Criticism: Delivering criticism in the best way, without hyperbole","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muzanni reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, heard me one day as I said, \u201cThis narrator is a great liar!\u201d Al-Shafi\u2019i said to me, \u201cO Abu Ibrahim, dress your words in the best manner. Do not say this narrator is a great liar, but rather say his narrations\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/05\/salat-nisa-hijab-wajib\/","url_meta":{"origin":20082,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Adult women must pray wearing veils","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe prayer of a menstruating woman is not accepted unless she wears a veil,\u201d by which he meant an adult woman. Imam al-Tirmidhi said, \"This is acted upon by the people of knowledge, that when a woman prays and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25785,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/shafiee-advice-private\/","url_meta":{"origin":20082,"position":3},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Nasihah: Sincere advice is given in private, not public","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muzanni reported: Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever admonishes his brother in private has been sincere to him and protected his reputation. Whoever admonishes him in public has humiliated him and betrayed him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 9\/140 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0632\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0638\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21512,"u